data.description: Gorgeous, updated Townhome near Garden of the Gods! Stunning Mountain views, and very quiet neighborhood.  Stainless steel appliances, ceramic tile, wood floors, granite countertops in bathrooms, custom lighting, plumbing, and sink fixtures throughout,  wood burning fireplace, well loved and maintained. The basement is fully finished and has been used as a separate studio apartment complete with a small kitchenette, large living space, laundry,  and 3/4 bath with own patio and separate entrance.  Buyer can leave as is for 2 living spaces or turn it back into one.   There is a covered parking space that is included a few feet away from the front door. Very convenient!   This home is close to schools, shopping, hospitals, and the great outdoors.  You will love watching the city lights at night, deer strolling by, and the clouds rolling in over Pike's Peak.  Very peaceful and tranquil. Wonderful location!
